data.description: BACK TO THE MARKET! This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom house is located on a cul-de-sac street with no neighbors on the rear or aside. The house is perfect for families who want to enjoy their privacy as it is located in a quiet neighborhood. The location is perfect with many shopping centers around and close to the I4. The house has been well-maintained and current owner has made important improvements in the back yard, also it has many features that will make you feel right at home. Come see this Perfect Starting home today!
